text: "Good Form" is a bounce/trap/hip hop song by Trinidadian-American rapper Nicki Minaj. It was released on August 10, 2018. It is from her fourth studio album, Queen. There was a remixed version that featured American rapper Lil Wayne. That remix was released on November 29, 2018. It peaked at number 60 on the Billboard Hot 100. It was written by Nicki Minaj and Mike Will Made It and Plush. A music video for the song was released on November 29, 2018. It was directed by Colin Tilley. It features Nicki Minaj and Lil Wayne, along with others. ==References== Category:2018 songs Category:Lil Wayne songs Category:Nicki Minaj songs
